title: Why does Catalonia want independence from Spain?
description: The drive for independence by the Spanish region of Catalonia is not a recent occurrence. Despite having their own language and culture, they have been part of Spain for centuries. So, why does a sizable part of its population yearns for independence? Why now? And why has the central Government response increased the tensions?
